      • of

        public static Event of(AggregateId aggregateId,
                       StreamTimestamp eventTimestamp,
                       UUID processingId,
                       VersionedName eventName,
                       Tuple parameters,
                       int... characteristics)
        Create a processed Event with the supplied properties.
        Parameters:
        aggregateId - The AggregateId of the aggregate to which the event occurred.
        eventTimestamp - The StreamTimestamp representing the time at which the event occurred.
        processingId - The processing UUID of the event (should be present only if the event has actually been processed). This must be a type 1 UUID, as it encodes the event's processing timestamp.
        eventName - The VersionedName of the event.
        parameters - The event's parameters.
        characteristics - The event's characteristics, e.g. whether it is an initial or terminal event.
        Returns:
        The constructed Event.
